Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.69,ZMXX,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,620)\frz333\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}否
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:43.94,ZW,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
